                A playful and cozy brand that blends two simple joys: the world's favorite morning beverage, coffee, and the world's largest, most laid-back rodent, the capybara. The name itself is a fusion of "kopi," meaning coffee in Indonesian, and "capybara," symbolizing the calm and relaxed vibe.
            </p>
            <div class="d-flex gap-3 mt-4">
                <a href="#about" class="btn btn-kopibara px-4 py-3">DISCOVER MORE</a>
                <a href="@Url.Action("Product", "Home")" class="btn py-3 px-4" style="background-color: transparent; color: #e0b07f; border: 1px solid #a35429; border-radius: 30px; transition: all 0.3s ease;">OUR MENU</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-7">
            <div class="position-relative">
                <img class="img-fluid" src="~/Images/KOPIBARA.png" alt="Kopibara Logo" style="filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2));" />
                <div class="position-absolute top-50 start-50 translate-middle" style="z-index: -1; width: 450px; height: 450px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(163,84,41,0.2) 0%, rgba(55,37,27,0) 70%);"></div>
